    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>2 AP </strong>and <strong>1 SP </strong>as a Reaction.</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger:</strong> You are the target of an<strong> Attack Check</strong> or <strong>Spell Check</strong>&nbsp;that targets <strong>PD</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Reaction:&nbsp;</strong>You can move up to your Speed and avoid the attack&nbsp;entirely as long as you end your movement outside the range&nbsp;or behind Full Cover of the <strong>Attack Check</strong> or <strong>Spell Check</strong>.</p>\n<p>Additional Opportunity Attacks are still able to be made&nbsp;against you when you Tumble and Dive.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Technique Enhancements</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Heroic Dive:</strong> <strong>(2 SP) </strong>You can bring 1 additional willing creature along with you as part of Tumble and Dive.&nbsp;They move the same amount of Spaces as you and must also end their movement within 1 Space of you.</li>\n</ul>",
